# $name

AiSOC **detection** plugin generated by `aisoc plugin new`.

## Layout

```
$slug/
├── plugin.yaml
├── README.md
└── rules/
    └── example.yaml   # add one YAML file per rule
```

Detection rules use the AiSOC schema (severity ladder is exactly
`info | low | medium | high`). See `detections/` in the AiSOC monorepo for
working examples across endpoint, network, cloud, identity, and application.

## Develop

```bash
aisoc plugin validate plugin.yaml
aisoc detection validate rules/example.yaml
```

## Publish

```bash
aisoc plugin publish .
```
